# ⚙️ Amazon Q Setup Guide

## 📌 Step 1: Create AWS Account
- Go to AWS official website
- Sign up with email
- Add billing details (free tier available)

---

## 📌 Step 2: Enable Amazon Q
- Open AWS Console
- Search for "Amazon Q Developer"
- Enable the service

---

## 📌 Step 3: Install AWS Toolkit

### For VS Code:
- Open Extensions
- Search "AWS Toolkit"
- Install it

---

## 📌 Step 4: Login to AWS
- Open AWS Toolkit
- Connect using IAM / credentials

---

## 📌 Step 5: Start Using Amazon Q
- Open command palette
- Start asking queries
- Use it for code, debugging, and cloud help

---

## ✅ Setup Completed!
